_sText: Fyseb_italia A Newer version has been released since this including fixes I can't remember and normal gameplay stuff. Gameplay Synopsis: Each team starts in a isolated room with 10 teleports in it. Each side marked from 1-5, which represent your "class". All the "classes" have two different spawn points. Classes/Equipment are as follows - 1. Infantry (CT) M4a1, (T) Ak47, USP, 1 HE, 1 Flash 2. Engineer M3 Shottie, Deagle, 1 Smoke, 1 HE 3. Recon (CT) TMP, (T) Mac10, P228 Compact, 2 Flash 4. Sniper Scout, USP, 2 Flashes 5. Heavy Gunner m249, Five-Seven, 1 Smoke, 1 HE Enjoy and have fun. -Sebhael
